<br>
If you don't at least have an epic pet, the mobs in PoP will chew your GV pets up in seconds.<br>
<br>
I think the 61 Air pet should have been on the vendor instead of the bolt.<br>
<br>
Level 65 magicians still looking for 61 spells will probably be fairly common soon.  There isn't much reason to be 61+ if you don't have the spells to go along with it.  <br>
<br>
It's kind of the same arguement we had in Kunark--<br>
LEVEL 52: THE DISCIPLINE OF EVASIVE <br>
LEVEL 53: THE DISCIPLINE OF CHARGE <br>
LEVEL 54: THE DISCIPLINE OF MIGHTY STRIKE <br>
LEVEL 55: THE DISCIPLINE OF DEFENSIVE <br>
LEVEL 56: THE DISCIPLINE OF FURIOUS <br>
LEVEL 57: THE DISCIPLINE OF PRECISION <br>
LEVEL 58: THE DISCIPLINE OF FELL STRIKE <br>
LEVEL 59: THE DISCIPLINE OF FORTITUDE <br>
LEVEL 60: THE DISCIPLINE OF AGGRESSIVE <br>
<br>
These are Warrior abilities that they achieve automatically when they level, while casters must go in search of rare drop only spells.<br>
